Retrieve flat files


Promoter sequences: promoter_sequences.fasta.gz [2.1 Mb]
This file contains the promoter sequences of all the genes described in the Yeastract database.

Gene sequences: gene_sequences.fasta.gz [2.8 Mb]
This file contains the genomic sequences of all the genes described in the Yeastract database.

Aminoacid sequences: aminoacid_sequences.fasta.gz [2.0 Mb]
This file contains the aminoacid sequences of all the proteins described in the Yeastract database.

Documented Regulations:
RegulationMatrix_Documented_2013927.csv.gz [288 Kb]
RegulationTwoColumnTable_Documented_2013927.tsv.gz [700 Kb]
These files contain the documented regulations between all transcription factors and genes described in the Yeastract database.

Transcription factor consensus list (TRANSFAC format): TFConsensusList_20130918.transfac.gz [20 Kb]
This file contains the transcription factor consensus list, in the TRANSFAC format, described in the Yeastract database.
